=============================================================
html skeleton

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<title>Hello World</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="main.css"> 
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>Hello World</h1>
		<p>This is a web page.</p>
	</body>
</html>


=============================================================
definition lists

<dl>
	<dt></dt>
	<dd>
	</dd>
</dl>

dl => definition list
dt => definition term
dd => definition description 
* you can add multiple definition terms to a definition description and vise versa
	inside the <dd></dd> you can also add <p> and other tags, but this is not allowed on <dt></dt>
	http://maxdesign.com.au/articles/definition/

=============================================================
css clearfix

.group:before,
	.group:after {
content: "";
display: table;
	}
.group:after {
clear: both;
}
.group {
	*zoom: 1;
}


